Body: Date: Thu, 21 Nov 1996 23:04:03 GMT Server: NCSA/1.4.2 Content-type: text/html Last-modified: Sat, 09 Nov 1996 02:40:38 GMT Content-length: 2955 Paul Tucker Paul Tucker Department of Computer Science and Engineering Mail Code 0114 University of California San Diego La Jolla, CA  92093  USA Last modification: 12 September 1996 Ephemeral quote The Economist, summing up the results of voting on 1996 ballot propositions: Money's usefulness apart, the moral of 1996 is clear: if you are a white male who wants to work for the minimum wage, bilk small investors and smoke joints when you're ill, California is the place to be.
